(670, 'What is chiefly omitted from this mythological version of October 1962 is what we sometimes call the Cuban , Cuban missile crisis: the physical and psychological reality faced during the crisis by everyone in Cuba, including the more than 43,000 Russians ', 'WP VBZ RB VBN IN DT JJ NN IN NNP CD VBZ WP PRP RB VBP DT JJ JJ NN NN DT JJ CC JJ NN VBN IN DT NN IN NN IN NNP VBG DT JJR IN CD NNPS', '5,6,16,4', NULL),
