(685, 'But the received wisdom was lopsidedly U', 'CC DT VBN NN VBD RB NNP', '1,3,5,4', NULL),
(686, 'For a quarter century after the crisis, Western scholars had virtually no access to Russian or Cuban sources either documents or senior officials responsible for making their governments'' key decisions during the crisis', 'IN DT NN NN IN DT NN JJ NNS VBD RB DT NN TO JJ CC JJ NNS CC NNS CC JJ NNS JJ IN VBG PRP$ NNS JJ NNS IN DT NN', '0,1,15,5', NULL),
