(733, 'It has influenced my opinion to see how this aggressive policy is developing, how the imperialists, disregarding world public opinion and ignoring principles of the law, are blockading the seas, violating our airspace and preparing an invasion, while at t', 'PRP VBZ VBN PRP$ NN TO VB WRB DT JJ NN VBZ VBG WRB DT NNS VBG NN JJ NN CC VBG NNS IN DT NN VBP VBG DT NNS VBG PRP$ NN CC VBG DT NN IN IN NN', '23,26,37,6', NULL),
