(743, 'We are now living our last minutes, perhaps hours, in calm equanimity, proud to provide you with a just cause for the annihilation of the United States, the leader of the entire imperialist world', 'PRP VBP RB VBG PRP$ JJ NNS RB NNS IN JJ NN NN TO VB PRP IN DT RB VB IN DT NN IN DT NNP NNPS DT NN IN DT JJ JJ NN', '5,9,17,10', NULL),
(744, 'Once more I convey to you the infinite gratitude and recognition of our people to the Soviet people who have been so generous and fraternal with us, as well as our profound gratitude and admiration for you, and wish you success in the huge task and seriou', 'RB RBR PRP VBP TO PRP DT JJ NN CC NN IN PRP$ NNS TO DT JJ NNS WP VBP VBN RB JJ CC JJ IN PRP RB RB IN PRP$ JJ NN CC NN IN PRP CC VB PRP NN IN DT JJ NN CC NN', '3,7,9,11', NULL),
(745, 'Please remember us, remember Cuba, when it comes time to write the history of the moment when righteous representatives of the oppressed resisted the Great Imperialist Entity, just before it was destroyed once and forever', 'VB VB PRP VB NNP WRB PRP VBZ NN TO VB DT NN IN DT NN WRB JJ NNS IN DT JJ VBD DT NNP NNP NNP RB IN PRP VBD VBN RB CC RB', '13,22,19,28', NULL),
(746, 'Less than two months after we first saw the letter, we participated in our Antigua conference, where Felix Kovaliev, head of the Russian Foreign Ministry Archives, added a chilling coda to Fidel''s Armageddon letter', 'RBR IN CD NNS IN PRP RB VBD DT NN PRP VBD IN PRP$ NNP NN WRB NNP NNP NN IN DT NNP NNP NNP NNPS VBD DT JJ NN TO NNP NNP NN', '7,8,30,3', NULL),
